    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏玩法</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>自动整理功能坏了，现在由你来承担整理玩家背包的任务。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>目标很简单：将相同的物品分组整理背包，获得你的奖励！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/11a4cf163c5c91312fbc476059617f99.poster.avif?t=1737643457\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/11a4cf163c5c91312fbc476059617f99.webm?t=1737643457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/11a4cf163c5c91312fbc476059617f99.mp4?t=1737643457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >现在玩家们纷纷来到你的商店，你将听到许多关于典型RPG/MMORPG玩家的故事，比如付费赢机制、不平衡的职业等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/e5117ffd32c230d7fff18501fbd37a2c.poster.avif?t=1737643457\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/e5117ffd32c230d7fff18501fbd37a2c.webm?t=1737643457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/e5117ffd32c230d7fff18501fbd37a2c.mp4?t=1737643457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >整理背包看似一项简单的任务，但随着玩家在世界中不断前进，越来越混乱的背包来到你的商店——还有不耐烦的冒险者。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/b490f9e9a7c4741b19bdf70a7f892446.poster.avif?t=1737643457\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/b490f9e9a7c4741b19bdf70a7f892446.webm?t=1737643457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/b490f9e9a7c4741b19bdf70a7f892446.mp4?t=1737643457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/e1417bedbc4067f05a405be9c9e97e6e.poster.avif?t=1737643457\" width=616 height=348 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/e1417bedbc4067f05a405be9c9e97e6e.webm?t=1737643457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/e1417bedbc4067f05a405be9c9e97e6e.mp4?t=1737643457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过整理背包获得的金币可以用来解锁秘密成就，揭开RPG/MMORPG世界的故事——一个开发者似乎只关心利润的地方。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/7959ce72679416599d4417fbce258bea.poster.avif?t=1737643457\" width=616 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/7959ce72679416599d4417fbce258bea.webm?t=1737643457\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201030/extras/7959ce72679416599d4417fbce258bea.mp4?t=1737643457\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >特征:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超过80个手工制作的背包，等待着整理。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >专为游戏设计的放松音乐和自定义音效。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >磨练你的空间技能，找到每个背包的最佳整理方式。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >享受幽默的时刻，听玩家们吐槽MMORPG游戏中常见的问题。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >跟随一个因开发者贪婪而逐渐死亡的MMORPG故事。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
